function serviceGroupBreakdownSection(){const rows=reportData(),groups=[['Men','men'],['Women','women'],['Youth','youth'],['Children','children'],['Campus','campus']],serviceTypes=[['Sunday Worship Service',s=>s.type.includes('Sunday')],['Monday Bible Study',s=>s.type.includes('Monday')],['Thursday Revival Hour',s=>s.type.includes('Thursday')]];const body=groups.map(([label,key])=>`<tr><td>${label.toUpperCase()}</td>${serviceTypes.map(([title,match])=>`<td>${rows.filter(match).reduce((a,s)=>a+(+s[key]||0),0)}</td>`).join('')}<td>${rows.reduce((a,s)=>a+(+s[key]||0),0)}</td></tr>`).join('');return `<section><h2>Attendance by group and service</h2><table><thead><tr><th>Group</th><th>Sunday Worship Service</th><th>Monday Bible Study</th><th>Thursday Revival Hour</th><th>Total</th></tr></thead><tbody>${body}</tbody></table></section>`}
function attendeeServiceSections(){const buckets={'Sunday Worship Service':[],'Monday Bible Study':[],'Thursday Revival Hour':[]},groupOrder=['Men','Women','Youth','Children','Campus'];people.forEach(p=>{if(!p.lastSeen)return;const day=new Date(p.lastSeen+'T12:00:00').getDay();if(day===0)buckets['Sunday Worship Service'].push(p);if(day===1)buckets['Monday Bible Study'].push(p);if(day===4)buckets['Thursday Revival Hour'].push(p)});const table=(title,items)=>{let serial=1;const rows=groupOrder.map(group=>{const groupPeople=items.filter(p=>p.group===group).sort((a,b)=>a.name.localeCompare(b.name));return groupPeople.length?`<tr class="note-row"><td colspan="3"><strong>${group.toUpperCase()}</strong></td></tr>${groupPeople.map(p=>`<tr><td>${serial++}</td><td>${p.name}</td><td>${p.group}</td></tr>`).join('')}`:''}).join('');return `<h3>${title}</h3><table><thead><tr><th>S/N</th><th>Name</th><th>Group</th></tr></thead><tbody>${rows||'<tr><td colspan="3">No named attendees recorded for this service day.</td></tr>'}</tbody></table>`};return `<section><h2>Attendee names by service attended</h2><p class="muted">Names are categorized from the People list using each person’s most recent recorded service date.</p>${table('Sunday Worship Service',buckets['Sunday Worship Service'])}${table('Monday Bible Study',buckets['Monday Bible Study'])}${table('Thursday Revival Hour',buckets['Thursday Revival Hour'])}</section>`}
attendeeServiceSections=function(){const buckets={'Sunday Worship Service':[],'Monday Bible Study':[],'Thursday Revival Hour':[]},groupOrder=['Men','Women','Youth','Children','Campus'];reportData().forEach(s=>{const key=s.type.includes('Sunday')?'Sunday Worship Service':s.type.includes('Monday')?'Monday Bible Study':s.type.includes('Thursday')?'Thursday Revival Hour':'';(s.attendees||[]).forEach(a=>{if(key)buckets[key].push({...a,date:s.date})})});const table=(title,items)=>{let serial=1;const rows=groupOrder.map(group=>{const groupPeople=items.filter(p=>p.group===group).sort((a,b)=>a.name.localeCompare(b.name));return groupPeople.length?`<tr class="note-row"><td colspan="4"><strong>${group.toUpperCase()}</strong></td></tr>${groupPeople.map(p=>`<tr><td>${serial++}</td><td>${p.name}</td><td>${p.group}</td><td>${fmtDate(p.date)}</td></tr>`).join('')}`:''}).join('');return `<h3>${title}</h3><table><thead><tr><th>S/N</th><th>Name</th><th>Group</th><th>Date</th></tr></thead><tbody>${rows||'<tr><td colspan="4">No named attendees recorded for this service in this report period.</td></tr>'}</tbody></table>`};return `<section><h2>Attendee names by service attended</h2><p class="muted">Names are pulled from the saved attendance register for each service in this report period.</p>${table('Sunday Worship Service',buckets['Sunday Worship Service'])}${table('Monday Bible Study',buckets['Monday Bible Study'])}${table('Thursday Revival Hour',buckets['Thursday Revival Hour'])}</section>`};
seniorReportHtml=function(){let html=seniorReportHtmlBase().replace('<h3>Senior Management Report</h3>',''),written=(html.match(/<section class="written"><h2>Written reports and summaries<\/h2>[\s\S]*?<\/section>/)||[''])[0];html=html.replace(written,'').replace(/<div class="two-col"><section><h2>Attendance by group<\/h2>[\s\S]*?<\/div><section><h2>Named attendees \/ roster<\/h2>/,`${written}${serviceGroupBreakdownSection()}<section><h2>Named attendees / roster</h2>`).replace(/<section><h2>Named attendees \/ roster<\/h2>[\s\S]*?<section><h2>Weekly breakdown<\/h2>/,`${attendeeServiceSections()}<section><h2>Weekly breakdown</h2>`);return html};
